OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777119066
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police called in
OL,4,Cafter van driven into gate at drone
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FCounter terrorism police have now
OL,8,Ftaken over the investigation into an
OL,9,Fincident which saw a van driven into a
OL,10,Fgate as protesters climbed onto the
OL,11,Froof of a drone factory in
OL,12,FLeicestershire.
OL,14,FLeicestershire Police was called at
OL,15,F3.10 am on Friday, April 24, to UAV
OL,16,FTactical Systems in Meridian Way,
OL,17,FBraunstone, following a report that a
OL,18,Fvan had been driven into a gate.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777119066
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police called in
OL,4,Cafter van driven into gate at drone
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FIt was reported that several
OL,8,Fprotesters had gained access to the
OL,9,Fbuilding's roof and were causing
OL,10,Fdamage.
OL,12,FTwo men had earlier been arrested at
OL,13,Fthe scene. A further four people were
OL,14,Fthen arrested.
OL,16,FThis means a total of six people have
OL,17,Fnow been arrested and remain in police
OL,18,Fcustody as of Friday afternoon:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777119066
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police called in
OL,4,Cafter van driven into gate at drone
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FA 41-year-old man arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to commit
OL,9,Fcriminal damage.
OL,11,FA 28-year-old man arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of causing criminal damage
OL,13,Fand assaulting an emergency worker.
OL,15,FA 27-year-old man arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of causing criminal damage.
OL,18,FA 28-year-old man arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of causing criminal damage.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
