OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777119066
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police called in
OL,4,Cafter van driven into gate at drone
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FA 25-year-old woman arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of causing criminal damage.
OL,10,FA 31-year-old woman arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of causing criminal damage.
OL,13,FAll six have also been arrested on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of conspiracy to commit
OL,15,Fburglary.
OL,17,FDue to the nature of this incident,
OL,18,FCounter Terrorism Policing East
OL,19,FMidlands is now leading the
OL,20,Finvestigation with the support of
OL,21,FLeicestershire Police.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
