FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777119066
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police called in
OL,4,Cafter van driven into gate at drone
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FOfficers said they remained at the
OL,8,Fscene at 4pm on Friday, April 24,
OL,9,Fwhile they continued to gather
OL,10,Fevidence and engage with those
OL,11,Fdirectly impacted by this incident.
OL,13,FAction group The After Shock has said
OL,14,Fit's responsible for the protest and
OL,15,Fclaims that UAV Tactical Systems'
OL,16,Fmajority shareholder Elbit Systems is
OL,17,F"Israel's biggest weapons maker" -
OL,18,Fsomething the company strongly denies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777119066
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police called in
OL,4,Cafter van driven into gate at drone
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FA spokesperson for UAV Tactical
OL,8,FSystems refuted the protesters'
OL,9,Fclaims. They said: "This group is
OL,10,Fusing misinformation as a tactic to
OL,11,Frecruit people to join them and commit
OL,12,Facts which could have serious legal
OL,13,Fconsequences.
OL,15,F"U-TacS provides critical support to
OL,16,Fthe UK armed forces. We do not supply
OL,17,Fthe Israeli military or Israeli
OL,18,FMinistry of Defence and any claims to
OL,19,Fthe contrary are completely false."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777119066
OL,3,CCounter terrorism police called in
OL,4,Cafter van driven into gate at drone
OL,5,Cfactory
OL,7,FLeicestershire Police said it
OL,8,Fcontinues to support the right to
OL,9,Fpeacefully protest but will also
OL,10,Fcontinue to take immediate action
OL,11,Fwhere reports of anyone seeking to
OL,12,Fcommit crime or damage to property are
OL,13,Fmade.
OL,15,FAnyone with information regarding this
OL,16,Fincident that may assist the
OL,17,Finvestigation can contact police on
OL,18,F101 quoting incident 65 of 24 April.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
